[
    {
        "text": "Now, on to something that's been all over the news in recent weeks,...",
        "startTime": 115,
        "endTime": 3521,
        "slowStartTime": 323,
        "slowEndTime": 5507
    },
    {
        "text": "...Elon Musk's purchase of Twitter.",
        "startTime": 3607,
        "endTime": 5649,
        "slowStartTime": 5560,
        "slowEndTime": 8699
    },
    {
        "text": "Yeah, his takeover hasn't been without issues, shall we say,...",
        "startTime": 5781,
        "endTime": 9243,
        "slowStartTime": 8821,
        "slowEndTime": 14090
    },
    {
        "text": "...from charging for verification, to laying off half of the social media site staff.",
        "startTime": 9399,
        "endTime": 13983,
        "slowStartTime": 14249,
        "slowEndTime": 21199
    },
    {
        "text": "As a result,...",
        "startTime": 14104,
        "endTime": 14878,
        "slowStartTime": 21306,
        "slowEndTime": 22542
    },
    {
        "text": "...millions of Twitter users are exploring another little-known platform called Mastodon.",
        "startTime": 14970,
        "endTime": 20692,
        "slowStartTime": 22605,
        "slowEndTime": 31263
    },
    {
        "text": "Our technology editor, Zoe Kleinman, gives us the low-down.",
        "startTime": 20974,
        "endTime": 24176,
        "slowStartTime": 31611,
        "slowEndTime": 36489
    },
    {
        "text": "It gets its name from a prehistoric elephant...",
        "startTime": 28288,
        "endTime": 31381,
        "slowStartTime": 42582,
        "slowEndTime": 47297
    },
    {
        "text": "...and shares it with a heavy metal band.",
        "startTime": 33641,
        "endTime": 37997,
        "slowStartTime": 50611,
        "slowEndTime": 57220
    },
    {
        "text": "Yes, Mastodon, an alternative to Twitter that's exploded in popularity lately.",
        "startTime": 40516,
        "endTime": 45724,
        "slowStartTime": 60924,
        "slowEndTime": 68811
    },
    {
        "text": "The first thing you have to do when you sign up is choose a server.",
        "startTime": 47647,
        "endTime": 50593,
        "slowStartTime": 71621,
        "slowEndTime": 76114
    },
    {
        "text": "There are loads of them,...",
        "startTime": 50819,
        "endTime": 51693,
        "slowStartTime": 76379,
        "slowEndTime": 77765
    },
    {
        "text": "...and they're themed by things like country, city, interests.",
        "startTime": 51771,
        "endTime": 55447,
        "slowStartTime": 77807,
        "slowEndTime": 83396
    },
    {
        "text": "You've got UK, Glasgow, gaming, and so on.",
        "startTime": 55540,
        "endTime": 59115,
        "slowStartTime": 83460,
        "slowEndTime": 88897
    },
    {
        "text": "It doesn't really matter which one you choose...",
        "startTime": 59327,
        "endTime": 60817,
        "slowStartTime": 89141,
        "slowEndTime": 91451
    },
    {
        "text": "...because you can see all the others anyway,...",
        "startTime": 60900,
        "endTime": 62373,
        "slowStartTime": 91500,
        "slowEndTime": 93785
    },
    {
        "text": "...but it gives you a sort of starting community of people...",
        "startTime": 62652,
        "endTime": 65355,
        "slowStartTime": 94128,
        "slowEndTime": 98257
    },
    {
        "text": "...who are more likely to be sharing the same sort of stuff...",
        "startTime": 65433,
        "endTime": 68006,
        "slowStartTime": 98299,
        "slowEndTime": 102234
    },
    {
        "text": "...that you're interested in as well.",
        "startTime": 68091,
        "endTime": 69971,
        "slowStartTime": 102287,
        "slowEndTime": 105181
    },
    {
        "text": "By the way, you don't tweet here, you Toot.",
        "startTime": 70438,
        "endTime": 73370,
        "slowStartTime": 105807,
        "slowEndTime": 110280
    },
    {
        "text": "One of the attractions of this platform is that it's decentralized.",
        "startTime": 74602,
        "endTime": 78161,
        "slowStartTime": 112053,
        "slowEndTime": 117466
    },
    {
        "text": "No one person or company owns Mastodon.",
        "startTime": 78425,
        "endTime": 81414,
        "slowStartTime": 117788,
        "slowEndTime": 122346
    },
    {
        "text": "The staffers all link up to form a kind of collective network,...",
        "startTime": 81751,
        "endTime": 85040,
        "slowStartTime": 122776,
        "slowEndTime": 127785
    },
    {
        "text": "...but they're all owned by individuals and different organizations.",
        "startTime": 85233,
        "endTime": 88471,
        "slowStartTime": 128000,
        "slowEndTime": 132931
    },
    {
        "text": "This does mean that you can be at the whim of whoever owns your server.",
        "startTime": 88807,
        "endTime": 92429,
        "slowStartTime": 133361,
        "slowEndTime": 138869
    },
    {
        "text": "If that goes down, so does your account.",
        "startTime": 92662,
        "endTime": 95100,
        "slowStartTime": 139143,
        "slowEndTime": 142875
    },
    {
        "text": "You can switch servers if you want to.",
        "startTime": 95414,
        "endTime": 97405,
        "slowStartTime": 143271,
        "slowEndTime": 146333
    },
    {
        "text": "But people are saying that it's quite a faff.",
        "startTime": 97711,
        "endTime": 99792,
        "slowStartTime": 146717,
        "slowEndTime": 149913
    },
    {
        "text": "There's also the issue of moderation.",
        "startTime": 100502,
        "endTime": 102455,
        "slowStartTime": 150903,
        "slowEndTime": 153907
    },
    {
        "text": "Because it's not centrally run, Mastodon moderation differs from server to server.",
        "startTime": 102567,
        "endTime": 106850,
        "slowStartTime": 154000,
        "slowEndTime": 160500
    },
    {
        "text": "Some have rules, some have none.",
        "startTime": 107123,
        "endTime": 108709,
        "slowStartTime": 160835,
        "slowEndTime": 163289
    },
    {
        "text": "It's free to use, but some of the hosts ask for donations because they don't get paid.",
        "startTime": 108989,
        "endTime": 113637,
        "slowStartTime": 163634,
        "slowEndTime": 170680
    }
]